        "Question": " Which of the following contracts of sale is void? a) Sale of EGM’s car by KRP, EGM’s agent, whose authority is not reduced into writing. b) Sale of EGM’s piece of land by KRP, EGM’s agent, whose authority is not reduced into writing. c) Sale of EGM’s car by KRP, a person stranger to EGM, without EGM’s consent or authority. d) Sale of EGM’s piece of land by KRP, a person stranger to EGM, without EGM’s consent or authority.",
