        "Answer": "YES, the child is entitled to the support and inheritance from Gigolo because a child, although illegitimate but recognized shall be entitled to support as well as successional rights from both of its parents. Gigolo voluntarily recognized the child, thus, the latter is rightfully entitled to be supported by Gigolo and to get his legitime upon the latter's death which is one-half of the legitime of a legitimate child."
