        "Answer": "There is no treachery as the attack was preceded by heated words. The act was spontaneous, arising from the said circumstance. The sudden attack was not preconceived and deliberately adopted but was just triggered by the sudden infuriation on the part of the accused, because of the provocative act of the victim, where their meeting was purely accidental."
