        "Answer": "Bruno should be sentenced to an indeterminate sentence penalty of arresto mayor in any of its period to prision correccional in its medium period as maximum. Bruno was entitled to two privileged mitigating circumstances of incomplete self-defense and the presence of at least two ordinary mitigating circumstances (voluntary surrender and plea of guilt) without any aggravating circumstance under Art. 69 and 64(5) of the RPC respectively, which lowers the prescribed penalty for homicide which is reclusion temporal to prision correccional."
