        "Answer": "Under the Indeterminate Sentence Law, the minimum of the sentence shall be anywhere within the range of 6 years and 1 day to 12 years imprisonment while the maximum of the sentence shall be anywhere within the range of Reclusion Temporal minimum i.e., not lower than 12 yrs. and 1 day to not more than 14 yrs. and 8 months."
