        "Question": "Dr. Chow, a government doctor, failed to submit his Daily Time Record (DTR)... The medical Director caused the withholding of his salary... Can Dr. Chow prosecute the medical director for causing him undue injury in violation of the Anti-Graft and Corrupt Practices Act? ",
