        "Answer": "Yes. Rigoberto is guilty of Direct Assault because the employment of violence was by reason of an actual performance of a duty by the offended party acting as a practicing lawyer. Lawyers are considered persons in authority by virtue of Batas Pambansa Big. 873... But the crime having been committed 10 years ago, may have already prescribed because it is punishable by a correctional penalty."
