        "No": 69,
        "Question": "Damian wants to know if he was unlawfully terminated. Explain. (1988 Bar Question)",
        "Answer": "Damian was unlawfully terminated. There could be just cause for his termination if his dishonesty and/or fraud are established, but there is no showing that the twin requirements of notice and hearing were observed by the company, hence the dismissal is illegal."
