        "Answer": "Patricio may file a Petition for Relief with preliminary injunction (Rule 38), posting a bond equivalent to the value of the property levied upon; or assail the levy as invalid if ground exists. Patricio may also simply pay the amount required by the writ and the costs incurred therewith."
